{"tid":1335210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋聞重溫】肥媽教食鯇魚魚生捱轟","createTime":"2019-07-20T12:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T12:07:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7be88b7937b76b50468eadd82b092331217131","tid":1335210,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:02:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190719/20732813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F20732813&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4sWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=09badb3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190719%2F20732813&h=3ff6efa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190719/20732813</a><br />\n<br />\n【蘋聞重溫】肥媽教食鯇魚魚生捱轟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190719/large/1563457490_905d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190719%2Flarge%2F1563457490_905d.jpg&h=36ee0752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李家鼎教煮狗食被質疑，其實無綫節目曾因介紹食品被鬧，上年10月肥媽Maria Cordero在節目中，兩度推介並大吃順德鯇魚魚生，通訊局隨後接獲7宗投訴，食安中心及衞生署衞生防護中心更在網上發文，強調「切勿進食淡水魚生」，除了有病菌外，還可能帶有寄生蟲，例如可造成膽管梗阻、肝硬化和引致膽管癌的中華肝吸蟲。<br />\n<br />\n另外，譚玉瑛去年12月主持節目中介紹食經淨化後的流浮山生蠔，節目出街後，食物安全中心在網上提醒市民，食用生蠔存有風險。  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：修哥出無綫活動風平浪靜<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n狗主轟無綫節目誤導通訊局收164宗投訴 李家鼎開鑊教煮狗食獸醫話錯晒<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n修哥出無綫活動風平浪靜<br />\n<br />\n修哥出無綫活動風平浪靜<br />\n張曦雯有諗過被圍<br />\n鄭家生爆粗鬧年輕人<br />\n狗主轟無綫節目誤導 通訊局收164宗投訴李家鼎開鑊教煮狗食 獸醫話錯晒"},{"pid":"4256ecc94b6b9e6b1e7f77e535e1f6274db9d932","tid":1335210,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:07:43.000Z","msg":"食左咪好似佢咁弱智囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}